QueryCallback.name: GetSupervisionOrdersEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: AGENCYCD = ? and DEFENDANT_ID LIKE ? and ORDERSTATUSCD != 'W' and ORDERSTATUSCD != 'I'

QueryCallback.name: GetOriginalSupervisionOrderEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: AGENCYCD = ? and CRIMINALCASE_ID = ? and VERSIONTYPECD = 'O' and ORDERSTATUSCD != 'W'

QueryCallback.name: ValidateNewOrderVersionEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: AGENCYCD = ? and CRIMINALCASE_ID = ? and ORDERCHAINNUM = ? and (VERSIONTYPECD = 'M' OR VERSIONTYPECD = 'A') AND (ORDERSTATUSCD = 'N' OR ORDERSTATUSCD = 'D' OR ORDERSTATUSCD = 'P')

QueryCallback.name: GetLatestInactiveSupervisionOrderEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: AGENCY_ID = ? AND DEFENDANT_ID = ? AND SPRVSIONPERIOD_ID = ? AND ORDERSTATUSCD = 'I' ORDER BY INACTIVEDATE DESC FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetLatestOrderChainNumForCaseEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: CRIMINALCASE_ID LIKE ? and ORDERSTATUSCD LIKE ? and AGENCYCD = ? ORDER BY ORDERCHAINNUM DESC FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetMostCurrentSupervisionOrderForCaseEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: CRIMINALCASE_ID LIKE ? and ORDERSTATUSCD LIKE ? and AGENCYCD = ? ORDER BY UPDATEDATE DESC FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetMostRecentInactiveOrderForSpnEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: ORDERSTATUSCD LIKE ? and AGENCYCD = ? and DEFENDANT_ID like ? ORDER BY INACTIVEDATE DESC

QueryCallback.name: GetMostRecentInactiveOrderForCaseEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: ORDERSTATUSCD = ? and AGENCYCD = ? AND CRIMINALCASE_ID = ? ORDER BY INACTIVEDATE DESC FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetSupervisionOrderVersionsEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: CRIMINALCASE_ID = ? and ORDERSTATUSCD != ? AND AGENCYCD = ? AND ORDERCHAINNUM=?

QueryCallback.name: GetAllSupervisionOrderVersionsEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: CRIMINALCASE_ID = ? and ORDERSTATUSCD != ? AND AGENCYCD = ? ORDER BY UPDATEDATE DESC

QueryCallback.name: GetCaseSupervisionPeriodEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: CRIMINALCASE_ID= ? AND AGENCYCD = ? AND (ORDERSTATUSCD = 'I' OR ORDERSTATUSCD = 'A')

QueryCallback.name: GetLastSupervisionOrderForPeriodQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: AGENCYCD = ? AND DEFENDANT_ID = ? AND SPRVSIONPERIOD_ID = ? AND SPVISIONENDDATE IS NOT NULL

QueryCallback.name: GetMigratedSupervisionOrderEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: AGENCYCD = ? and CRIMINALCASE_ID = ? and ORDERCHAINNUM = ? AND VERSIONTYPECD = ? AND CREATEJIMS2USER LIKE 'MIG-%' AND ORDERSTATUSCD = 'I'

QueryCallback.name: ValidateConditionInUseEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: CONDITION_ID = ? ORDER BY CONDITION_ID offset 0 rows fetch next 1 ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetSupervisionPeriodForComplianceEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: DEFENDANT_ID = ? and AGENCY_ID = ? AND SPRVISIONENDDATE IS NULL FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetActiveSupervisionPeriodQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: DEFENDANT_ID = ? and AGENCY_ID = ? AND SPRVISIONENDDATE IS NULL

QueryCallback.name: GetPriorSupervisionPeriodsQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: DEFENDANT_ID = ? AND AGENCY_ID LIKE ? AND SPRVISIONENDDATE IS NOT NULL
